<h1>
<span> <a href="//yro.slashdot.org/story/24/11/12/2238200/discord-leaker-sentenced-to-15-years-in-prison">Discord Leaker Sentenced To 15 Years In Prison</a> <span><a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/pentagon-leaker-jack-teixeira-sentenced-15-years-prison-sharing-milita-rcna179792" title="External link - https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/pentagon-leaker-jack-teixeira-sentenced-15-years-prison-sharing-milita-rcna179792" target="_blank"> (nbcnews.com) </a></span></span>
