<span> <a href="//science.slashdot.org/story/24/11/12/0211208/spacex-to-attempt-daring-orbital-refueling-test-of-starship">SpaceX To Attempt Daring Orbital Refueling Test of Starship</a> <span><a href="https://gizmodo.com/spacex-to-attempt-daring-orbital-refueling-test-of-starship-2000520122" title="External link - https://gizmodo.com/spacex-to-attempt-daring-orbital-refueling-test-of-starship-2000520122" target="_blank"> (gizmodo.com) </a></span></span>
<span><a href="//science.slashdot.org/story/24/11/12/0211208/spacex-to-attempt-daring-orbital-refueling-test-of-starship#comments">95</a></span>
